```mermaid
    A[Web Browser] --> B[FastAPI Application]

```

### 

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class FastAPIApp {
        +startup()
        +include_router()
        +mount_static()
    }
    
    class DatabaseManager {
        +init_database()
        +get_connection()
        +CRUD_operations()
        +query_functions()
    }
    
    class PriceFetcher {
        +detect_symbol_type()
        +fetch_price()
        +multi_source_fallback()
    }
    
    class RouterHandlers {
        +overview_routes()
        +transaction_routes()
        +holding_routes()
        +settings_routes()
        +api_routes()
    }
    
    FastAPIApp --> RouterHandlers
    RouterHandlers --> DatabaseManager
    RouterHandlers --> PriceFetcher
    DatabaseManager --> SQLite
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebUI
    participant API
    participant Database
    participant PriceAPI
```
